com.textmagic.sms.dto
Class MessageStatus

java.lang.Object
  com.textmagic.sms.dto.MessageStatus

public class MessageStatus
extends java.lang.Object

The data transfer object MessageStatus is representation of message delivering status.

The main attributes are:

  • message - the message object, whose status this object represents
  • deliveryState - current state of delivering progress. see MessageStatus.DeliveryState
  • createdTime - the Date when sms was created
  • replyNumber - the phone number (MSISDN) the message recipient can reply to. See Reply options
  • creditsCost - the cost of the sent message. the value will be provided only if delivering completed (the deliveryState is final.)
  • completedTime - the Date when delivering was completed. the value will be provided only if delivering is over (the deliveryState is final)

Author:
Rafael Bagmanov
